data.description: Excellent property for your first time buyers. This one is located in a very quiet area of Lake Elsinore. This area features public parks, stores, theaters, easy access to the 15 FWY and many other advantages. The property features lots of rooms, huge living room, and is very well taken care in the interior. Beautiful backyard with lots of space, wood floors all over the place. Come and see with your buyers!!
